name: Verde
biography: Born on February 18, 2005, Verde, a burgeoning Albanian artist living in Athens, Greece, made his first appearance in the Greek music scene in 2022 with his bilingual abilities blending both Albanian and Greek rap cultures. With only seven releases under his name, Verde's breakthrough came with MOTORA, a record-breaking track for him that catapulted Verde into the spotlight in the Greek music industry in the fourth quarter of 2023. In 2024, he further cemented his place in the industry with the release of his hit song ARAI, 6 months later he released his single POLICIA featuring Fy. He is also featured on Kidd's debut album BABYSHARK with the song titled KARMA. Currently signed to Capital Music and Minos EMI a Universal Music Company, his authentic blend of afro-trap and hip-hop resonated with audiences, showcasing a versatility that defied his newcomer status. Verde's impact on the Greek music landscape is undeniable, marking him as a rising star with boundless potential for the future.
